snippet.textDisplay:
Allah's Messenger (ﷺ) said, "Allah has ninety-nine Names, one-hundred less one; and he who memorized them all by heart will enter Paradise."
Sahih al-Bukhari 7392
snippet.textOriginal:
Allah's Messenger (ﷺ) said, "Allah has ninety-nine Names, one-hundred less one; and he who memorized them all by heart will enter Paradise."
Sahih al-Bukhari 7392

snippet.textDisplay:
Here are the 99 Names of Allah (Asmaul Husna):

*1-10*

1. Ar-Rahman (الرحمن) - The All-Compassionate
2. Ar-Rahim (الرحيم) - The All-Merciful
3. Al-Malik (المالك) - The King
4. Al-Quddus (القدوس) - The Holy
5. As-Salam (السلام) - The Peace
6. Al-Mu'min (المؤمن) - The Faithful
7. Al-Muhaymin (المهيمن) - The Guardian
8. Al-'Aziz (العزيز) - The Mighty
9. Al-Jabbar (الجبار) - The Compeller
10. Al-Mutakabbir (المتكبر) - The Majestic

*11-20*

1. Al-Khaliq (الخالق) - The Creator
2. Al-Bari' (البارئ) - The Evolver
3. Al-Musawwir (المصور) - The Fashioner
4. Al-Ghaffar (الغفار) - The Forgiver
5. Al-Qahhar (القهار) - The Subduer
6. Al-Wahhab (الوهاب) - The Bestower
7. Ar-Razzaq (الرزاق) - The Provider
8. Al-Fattah (الفتاح) - The Opener
9. Al-'Alim (العليم) - The Knower
10. Al-Qabid (القابض) - The Withholder

*21-30*

1. Al-Basit (الباسط) - The Expander
2. Al-Khafid (الخافض) - The Abaser
3. Ar-Rafi' (الرافع) - The Exalter
4. Al-Mu'izz (المعز) - The Honorer
5. Al-Mudhill (المذل) - The Humiliator
6. As-Sami' (السميع) - The Hearer
7. Al-Basir (البصير) - The Seer
8. Al-Hakam (الحكم) - The Judge
9. Al-'Adl (العادل) - The Just
10. Al-Latif (اللطيف) - The Gentle

*31-40*

1. Al-Khabir (الخبير) - The Aware
2. Al-Halim (الحليم) - The Forbearing
3. Al-'Azim (العظيم) - The Magnificent
4. Al-Ghafur (الغفور) - The Forgiving
5. Ash-Shakur (الشكور) - The Thankful
6. Al-'Ali (العلي) - The High
7. Al-Kabir (الكبير) - The Great
8. Al-Hafiz (الحفيظ) - The Preserver
9. Al-Muqit (المقيت) - The Nourisher
10. Al-Hasib (الحسيب) - The Reckoner

*41-50*

1. Al-Jalil (الجليل) - The Majestic
2. Al-Karim (الكريم) - The Generous
3. Ar-Raqib (الرقيب) - The Watcher
4. Al-Mujib (المجيب) - The Responder
5. Al-Wasi' ( الواسع) - The All-Encompassing
6. Al-Hakim (الحكيم) - The Wise
7. Al-Wadud (الودود) - The Loving
8. Al-Majid (المجيد) - The Glorious
9. Al-Ba'ith (الباعث) - The Resurrector
10. Ash-Shahid (الشهد) - The Witness

*51-60*

1. Al-Haqq (الحق) - The Truth
2. Al-Wakil (الوكيل) - The Trustee
3. Al-Qawi (القوي) - The Strong
4. Al-Matin (المتين) - The Firm
5. Al-Wali (الوالي) - The Protector
6. Al-Hamid (الحميد) - The Praiseworthy

10. Al-Muhyi (المحيي) - The Giver of Life

*61-70*

1. Al-Mumit (المميت) - The Taker of Life
2. Al-H
